messageBody:
Everyone:

Since spam has not previously been a significant problem, let's wait a
little before adopting an approval method for new members. I agree with
Ewout: we don't want to set up procedures that might prove to be
barriers to people learning about QS unless it is absolutely necessary.

Hugh -- loved your pseudo-latin.

Paige Gabhrt
